Author: nemesisdani
Text: I'm on vyvanse 60mg for BED. It makes me nauseated on and off throughout the day so I eat less but by evening and night I'm often starving and just make up for doing well during the day :( The nausea is pretty awful too so I dont really feel.tempted to abuse it. I just wish it worked...I havent really.lost anything and it's been 3 months

Author: DuckieIsMyHero88
Text: I'm on Vyvannse for Adhd. While I think I need to up mine, I find it does help with wanting to eat. Though on the days I don't take it I'm always hungry so be careful of that
